author: Colin Bowles
title: Logano Takes Checkered in Kansas
text:
Logano Takes Checkered in Kansas - WVVA TV Bluefield Beckley WV News, Weather and Sports Member Center: Logano Takes Checkered in Kansas Posted: Follow @ColinxBowles 
The case landed at Kanas speedway Sunday for the chase. Joey Logona took the checkered for his second win in a row. He angered fellow driver, Matt Kensenth as with 5 laps to go he spun Kenseth out while he was leading. Kyle Busch, Ryan Newman, Dale Earnhardt Jr, Matt Kenseth are the four drivers on the outside looking in to the chase.
